                <span>友情链接：</span>
                <a href="http://www.qq.com/" target="_blank">TECENT腾讯</a>
                <a href="http://www.huigur.com/" target="_blank">域名空间</a>
                <a href="http://www.tencent.com/" target="_blank">腾讯网络</a>
